The health ingredients market is competitive, with several key players dominating the industry. ADM, DuPont, and DSM are among the leading companies offering a wide range of health ingredients for various applications. Lonza specializes in innovative solutions for the pharmaceutical and healthcare sectors. Kerry Group focuses on taste and nutrition solutions, catering to consumer preferences. Ingredion offers ingredient solutions for the food and beverage industry, with a focus on clean label and natural products. BASF and Cargill provide a diverse portfolio of health ingredients for different industries. Tate & Lyle specializes in sweeteners and texturants for food and beverages. Arla Foods is a key player in the dairy ingredients segment, offering high-quality proteins and calcium-rich ingredients.

